# 🚀 Spring Boot REST API - Learning Project

This repository contains my first Spring Boot REST API project developed using **Spring Tool Suite (STS)** and tested using **Postman**.

## 📚 About the Project

This project was created as part of my Spring Boot learning journey. It demonstrates how to create and test REST APIs using Spring Boot.

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- Java 21
- Spring Boot
- Spring Tool Suite (STS)
- Maven
- Postman

## 📁 Features

- Spring Boot project setup
- REST Controller
- GET API
- POST API
- PUT API
- DELETE API
- JSON Request & Response
- API Testing using Postman

## 📌 REST Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/products` | Get all products |
| POST | `/products` | Create a product |
| PUT | `/products/{id}` | Update a product |
| DELETE | `/products/{id}` | Delete a product |

## ▶️ How to Run

1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/product-management.git
```

2. Open in Spring Tool Suite (STS)

3. Run the application

4. Open Postman and test APIs

Base URL

```
http://localhost:8080
```

